# Get Those Groceries.

Welcome aboard <%= @user.name %>, Supermarkit is here to try and help make your grocery shopping **simpler**, and **better**.

# We
As a bunch of software students we decided that there must be a more efficient way than using an excel document to keep track of our eating habits. Supermarkit brings together you and your friends into groups of shoppers that can unite and overcome the hastle of organizing group or individual grocery shopping.

# Shop
Supermarkit let's you keep track of the groceries you have bought and are planning to buy with ease. It knows that if every week you by *bread*, you're probably going to buy *bread* again and makes it easy to re-add familiar items.

# Together
Don't take our word for it, [try out Supermarkit](<%= activate_user_url(@user.activation_token) %>) and let us know what you think. If you see an itch that you would desperately like to accommodate, talk to us through our email link on the site or reply to this email to get in contact. We want to know how to make SuperMarkit something you would like to use for your grocery shopping on a regular basis.

Thanks.